Fortis roa, strength and breath,

387
00:27:18,970 --> 00:27:20,750
Strength and breath, strength and breath.

388
00:27:20,750 --> 00:27:23,170
William Hooke, thou art the dead I seek.

389
00:27:23,170 --> 00:27:25,500
William Hooke, answer my calling.

390
00:27:25,500 --> 00:27:28,520
Strength and breath, strength and breath, strength and breath.

391
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:36,990
You.

392
00:27:36,990 --> 00:27:37,880
Yes.

393
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:42,000
I thought our business concluded.

394
00:27:42,310 --> 00:27:44,100
Tell me John Alden's secret.

395
00:27:48,460 --> 00:27:51,230
Meet me in hell, you bitch.

396
00:27:51,230 --> 00:27:53,620
Oh, there are worse places than hell.

397
00:27:54,230 --> 00:27:55,210
Speak!

398
00:28:34,060 --> 00:28:36,230
Witch!

399
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:39,410
Oh, no, Emily.

400
00:28:40,450 --> 00:28:41,440
It's your father.

401
00:29:01,020 --> 00:29:02,140
What's happened now?

402
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:05,710
Query your mistress. I haven't the faintest idea.

403
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,250
What of your mission?

404
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,650
Of course I find you here,

405
00:29:23,290 --> 00:29:26,380
Not at the jail investigating this new witch,

406
00:29:26,380 --> 00:29:27,840
Not with Mercy Lewis,

407
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:32,230
But here, alone, playing with your blasted toys.

408
00:29:32,230 --> 00:29:35,050
It seems I am determined to displease you, Mrs. Sibley.

409
00:29:42,940 --> 00:29:43,980
Mrs. Sibley.

410
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,500
Please.

411
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:51,570
- I'm sorry - Please.

412
00:29:56,040 --> 00:29:57,540
Tell me... what troubles you.

413
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:03,370
That girl has gone mad with power.

414
00:30:04,690 --> 00:30:08,820
Encouraged by her peers, influenced by petty dispute.

415
00:30:10,570 --> 00:30:14,260
The selectmen fear that she's no longer reliable.

416
00:30:15,100 --> 00:30:16,440
Nonsense.

417
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:18,650
They are uncertain that she can be further trusted.

418
00:30:18,650 --> 00:30:20,540
It is not theirs to decide.

419
00:30:21,170 --> 00:30:22,030
I will assess the girl

420
00:30:22,030 --> 00:30:23,940
and form my own opinion of her role.

421
00:30:24,930 --> 00:30:26,160
You would do that, reverend?

422
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,090
Of course.

423
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:33,940
I am torn and harried by my many responsibilities.

424
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:36,730
It's my fault completely.

425
00:30:38,470 --> 00:30:40,590
I hadn't considered the toll this has taken on you.

426
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:44,190
Oh, and a rift amongst the selectmen at this fragile moment

427
00:30:44,190 --> 00:30:47,930
might be more burden than I... or salem...could bear.

428
00:30:49,020 --> 00:30:50,340
Worry not, Mrs. Sibley.

429
00:30:50,970 --> 00:30:52,840
You fetched me here to run these witch trials,

430
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:54,860
and run them I must.

431
00:31:00,370 --> 00:31:01,670
Thank you, reverend.

432
00:31:02,340 --> 00:31:03,380
What a relief to find

433
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:05,930
at least one who can relieve my hardships.

434
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:19,050
What is that?

435
00:31:22,030 --> 00:31:25,750
It's an artifact that I'm researching.

436
00:31:32,010 --> 00:31:33,980
Does it have to do with witches?

437
00:31:35,080 --> 00:31:36,900
It's associated with the grand rite,

438
00:31:37,610 --> 00:31:41,480
a ritual of death attributed to witches over the centuries.

439
00:31:42,770 --> 00:31:46,150
And why does this object in particular concern you?

440
00:31:48,210 --> 00:31:50,450
Everything regarding witches concerns me, madam.

441
00:31:51,890 --> 00:31:53,530
We cannot be too prepared.

442
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:08,220
What luck for Salem that your father was unavailable.

443
00:32:09,250 --> 00:32:11,740
