531
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:51,670
I lied to you earlier.

532
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:54,730
I was young once --

533
00:38:55,770 --> 00:38:58,850
young enough that I believed in goodness.

534
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:02,270
I believed in it because I saw it in you.

535
00:39:03,230 --> 00:39:06,300
You can't help it. Y-you can't stop it.

536
00:39:07,070 --> 00:39:08,570
You can't be any other way.

537
00:39:10,580 --> 00:39:12,170
And I think that's why I loved you.

538
00:39:15,810 --> 00:39:17,370
Imagine my surprise...

539
00:39:18,570 --> 00:39:21,770
being told you're a murderer.

540
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:27,520
You don't know me.

541
00:39:28,900 --> 00:39:29,660
What?

542
00:39:30,850 --> 00:39:32,210
You don't know me!

543
00:39:34,290 --> 00:39:37,250
- I killed 20 men. - No.

544
00:39:37,250 --> 00:39:38,900
Yes. 20 men.

545
00:39:38,900 --> 00:39:41,590
And their only crime was that they had come to save me.

546
00:39:41,590 --> 00:39:42,500
No, I won't believe it.

547
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:43,900
Believe it because it's true!

548
00:39:52,470 --> 00:39:54,830
Lucky men go to their graves with no regrets.

549
00:39:58,220 --> 00:40:00,650
Barely a day passes when I don't have one.

550
00:40:08,410 --> 00:40:10,950
Sometimes in life, we make choices.

551
00:40:12,640 --> 00:40:15,580
And sometimes, these -- these difficult choices --

552
00:40:15,580 --> 00:40:19,020
they lead us to do things, terrible things,

553
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:21,010
and we don't wish to.

554
00:40:21,700 --> 00:40:23,800
We'd do anything not to.

555
00:40:25,180 --> 00:40:26,980
But choice informs choice.

556
00:40:28,330 --> 00:40:29,950
Your actions, though your own,

557
00:40:30,410 --> 00:40:31,200
They -- they don't resemble

558
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:33,380
anything you'd have wanted or wished for.

559
00:40:35,380 --> 00:40:37,350
Tell me that it was like that,

560
00:40:37,630 --> 00:40:41,570
