561
00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:44,450
a terrible thing, please, please,

562
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:47,980
So that I might still believe in goodness.

563
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:00,910
I murdered 20 men.

564
00:41:03,310 --> 00:41:05,590
And I make no excuses for myself.

565
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:13,670
Will you have me arrested?

566
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:21,130
I am the only one that knows.

